I say that these bible haters, these evolutionists, are brewers of poison! and the legislature of this sovereign state has had the wisdom to demand that the peddlers of poison, in bottles or in books, clearly label the product they attempt to sell.
I say that if this law is not upheld, this boy will become one of a generation shorn of its faith by the teachings of godless science!
But, if the full penalty of the law is meted out to Bertram Cates, the faithful the whole world over who are watching us here and listening to our every word will rise up and call this courtroom blessed!
