- Get up!
- Aren't you scared?
Stop!
Come back!
Come here!
Throw them the chains as a reminder.
Take the horses to where the stream branches.
Don't move until I say so.
Take Jifi with you.
No, I'll send Mikoléé
Hence!
I said silence!
Have them take the lamb!
Why do you constantly try me?
Why can I not swallow my sinful saliva?
Whores!
In the name of God and the King, yeoman Kozlik, known as "Goat. "
The guardian of justice speaks with you.
Our Lord and King.
Open the gate and lay down your arms. Your iniquity is over.
Go back to Boleslav!
My gates are strong, and I've lost the key!
You have wronged the next Bishop of Hennau.
The King demands to know what you have done with him.
Answer, and give yourself up!
Listen, Captain.
The King is the lord of us all.
But war is the lord of kings.
War is the judge of my actions.
I may defeat your troops and talk with the king's envoy.
Perhaps I will be defeated and killed.
The right of victory will decide.
May your message be carried away by the wind.
- Halt!
- War is declared, and I have no scribe!
Thieving louts!
If you do not yield, you will be killed!
And your family will starve!
Before I storm your castle,
I'll kill one of yours as a warning
I know nothing of the Emperor!
We will bargain!
If you wrong my son, they'll need a new bishop!
What are you waiting for?
Finish him off!
Get back. Don't move!
Kill him, father!
Form a line!
Line up!
Get back!
Line up!
Here you are!
Stupid, mangy, asses... !
