I've been expecting you.
You are pale, sir.
Have you been ill?
Yes, my lady... ill.
Drink, Armin.
This is honey.
-Is it bitter?
-Thank you, my lady.
You thanked her without looking at her.
Members of the Order don't look at woman.
That belongs to the past.
Stay with us, Armin.
You can rest.
We can go hunting together.
You can have my dogs.
