Here, here, here and here.
Second rule, go for the cripple before the slow kill.
Here's a slow kill on the yellow.
Here, here and here.
Remember, a slow kill may have enough left in him to kill you before he dies.
With a cripple, you know you've got him if you keep your distance and wear him down.
