Real intentions?
Yes, your real intentions.
My dissolute life is to deceive the shogunate.
We can prove our loyalty only by restoring the Asano Clan.
You know I'm going to my death, will you still lie to me?
Our lord, goaded beyond endurance, knowingly sacrificed his clan.
They made him die like a criminal.
I believe in you, Chamberlain.
I'm going to die.
Please tell me the truth!
Sampei, I have formed the habit of doubting people.
I couldn't make up my mind.
Up till this moment I have wavered.
But your words have decided me.
Then...?
I will defy the shogunate.
Chamberlain!
You have my word.
Saburoji? Come in, it's open.
You brought seconds?
That wasn't necessary.
Sampei! It's time. Come out!
You're it. Come to the clapping.
I caught you!
Hara and Onodera? Did you pay my bill here for me?
Yes.
I see. Then let's drink.
The money man's here.
He'll buy you whatever you want.
Sampei Kayano committed harakiri.
I see.
What's wrong?
Nothing. I just heard that my pet sparrow died.
Sparrow?
Oh, yes.
Let's hold a wake for it tonight.
I'll be the chief abbot.
You play the samisen and pray.
