Cry, all of you, cry. Cry!
The Shogun has banished
Lord Daigaku to Hiroshima for life.
We must hurry. Kira's rank is high, but his holdings small.
But the great Uesugi Clan is behind him.
If we 61 who signed the pact are united, we have nothing to fear.
