A carpenter has been told to build secret passages and hiding places.
Okano's trying to get the plans.
Kujuro, were you a samurai?
Yes, but I hated it from childhood.
Always duty, loyalty...
I wanted freedom, so I became a commoner.
What about your parents?
They gave up and told me to marry and do as I please.
Found a nice bride?
Yes.
Really?
I haven't asked her, but my mind's made up.
