We're not just after Kira's head.
You should know that!
Do not act on impulse.
Are you safe? There are many of Asano's men in Edo.
I had to come when I heard that a fire had struck your home.
No, no, it's made me richer.
Something shining under the gifts of condolence?
The elders and lords all sent me trees and rare garden stones.
I don't know why.
Like some? Is your new home done?
Oh, it's you.
Look, lend me the plans a few days.
What for?
Kujuro wants to borrow it.
Why would a rice shop man want it?
To boast that I'm the sister of the man who built this fine house.
I see. For my dear sister's sake.
You will? Thank you.
Yes, of course. That's what
