You shall be shut away in the country.
It’s you then, and not Wolsey, who really wants this thing.
I will have it!
I too gave evidence that my marriage to Arthur was never consummated.
Did I lie to the Pope all those years ago?
Did I lie to God?
Did I lie to you?
No.
I will live and I will die your wife.
And your Queen.
